These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, comedy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
3. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking juice##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | juice  | 7up   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | musical   |
| Sport         | biathlon | skateboarding |
| Transport     | scooter | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peach, lime
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, superhero
2 different pets are kept: lizard, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, helicopter
1. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person eating lime is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | peach     | lime |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | satire  |
| Pet           | cat         | lizard     |
| Transport     | roller   | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
