The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, software-developer
2 different pets are kept: turtle, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway
1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the software-developer##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Job         | software-developer | security-guard    |
| Pet         | turtle         | goat        |
| Transport   | quad-bike         | subway    |

