.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, scientist
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, nigerian
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
2. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the scientist is the japanese##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | scientist | paramedic    |
| Nationality   | japanese       | nigerian |
| Pet           | guinea-pig         | dog    |
| Sport         | rugby    | handball   |

